<h1>Protestos de servidores em todo país exigem direitos - A Nova Democracia</h1>
<p>Author: Giovanna Maria</p>
<p>Description: Servidores públicos municipais têm realizado greves exigindo  reajustes salariais, melhores condições de trabalho e rechaçando reformas anti-povo.</p>
<p>Publish Time: 2023-03-02T16:31:43-03:00</p>
<p>Modified Time: 2023-03-02T16:36:59-03:00</p>
<p>Updated Time: 2023-03-02T16:36:59-03:00</p>
<p>Images: ['<a href="https://anovademocracia.com.br/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/sintrapp-1.webp">sintrapp-1.webp</a>', '<a href="https://anovademocracia.com.brdata:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxMDIxIiBoZWlnaHQ9Ijc2OCIgdmlld0JveD0iMCAwIDEwMjEgNzY4Ij48cmVjdCB3aWR0aD0iMTAwJSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxMDAlIiBzdHlsZT0iZmlsbDojY2ZkNGRiO2ZpbGwtb3BhY2l0eTogMC4xOyIvPjwvc3ZnPg==">svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSIxMDIxIiBoZWlnaHQ9Ijc2OCIgdmlld0JveD0iMCAwIDEwMjEgNzY4Ij48cmVjdCB3aWR0aD0iMTAwJSIgaGVpZ2h0PSIxMDAlIiBzdHlsZT0iZmlsbDojY2ZkNGRiO2ZpbGwtb3BhY2l0eTogMC4xOyIvPjwvc3ZnPg==</a>']</p>
